annotation:
1，判断客户风险状态
case when a.hedge_real_exch_risk_degree <  1.0 then  '强平状态'   
                     when a.hedge_real_risk_degree      <  1.0  and  a.hedge_real_exch_risk_degree >= 1.0 then '追保状态'
                     when a.hedge_real_risk_degree      >  1.0  and  a.hedge_real_risk_degree      <  1.2 
                      and a.hedge_real_exch_risk_degree >= 1.0 then  '预警状态'
                end  as risk_stat
2，取出强平状态的客户数
case when risk_stat='追保状态' then count(client_id)

select p.client_id
       ,p.fund_account
       ,p.money_type
       ,count(p.init_date) as day_count
   from (select client_id
               ,fund_account
               ,money_type
               ,init_date
               ,count(1)

(select a.period_id,
       case when srp_kind='0' then 4 else 6 end as credit_type_id,
       a.client_id,
       funder_type,
       round(d.asset / 1.0, 4) + sum(a.zcje) over(partition by a.period_id, a.client_id) as total_asset,
       round((d.asset * 1.0 + sum(a.zcje) over(partition by a.period_id, a.client_id)) / sum(a.hxfz) over(partition by a.period_id, a.client_id),4) as total_ass_Rate
